<p style="text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:-16px;margin-bottom:24px;"><em>Khu c\u0103n h\u1ED9 cao c\u1EA5p v\u1EDBi thi\u1EBFt k\u1EBF hi\u1EC7n \u0111\u1EA1i t\u1EA1i khu Th\u1EE7 Thi\xEAm</em></p>

