  <li><strong>C\u0103n h\u1ED9 trung \u2013 cao c\u1EA5p t\u1EA1i Bi\xEAn H\xF2a:</strong> Nhu c\u1EA7u \u1EDF th\u1EF1c t\u1EEB h\xE0ng tr\u0103m ngh\xECn chuy\xEAn gia k\u1EF9 thu\u1EADt cao trong c\xE1c KCN.</li>
